description: Established in 1987 from the peripheral blood of a patient with T-cell acute lymphoblastic leukemia (T-ALL) obtained two months prior to her death. May be of value in evaluating the role of t(16;20) in the etiology of T-ALL.
health_status: T-cell acute lymphoblastic leukemia cell line ATCC CRL-2629
summary: Homo sapiens Loucy immortalized cell line
